src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女發現佢不斷叫自己上去探老母，次次都帶入房扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女終於發覺唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解佢扑完就唔點理自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 說好的浪漫呢？於是提出分手，佢當然唔挽留，因為蝦條已呃，搵下一個目標算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條仔得罪你咩</blockquote><br />\n我話條女好地地同男朋友分手<br />\n搞到而家咁抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c485f8d5c02a7d4738a2fd7a3f4230a12400d24","tid":348181,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T19:50:20.000Z","msg":"呢種賤女人 <br />\n唔比呢個屌都比第個屌嫁啦<br />\n比人哄下就飛左條仔<br />\n比人中出飛係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開香檳就差唔多<br />\n如果男事主見到呢個post麻煩公開條女張相<br />\n廢事其他巴打再比呢個水性楊花嘅女人呃到"},{"pid":"bdeacda29ce41f0e86fdd0a96dc8d9c0b5575660","tid":348181,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T20:11:59.000Z","msg":"啱啦呢啲臭閪係要比人當肉便器玩下架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e78c2d480db5908b7026989d011fd1aa371a03","tid":348181,"uid":32721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T20:18:39.000Z","msg":"男事主出黎爆下料"},{"pid":"06a36879f9e316a511313f036751c153074be334","tid":348181,"uid":27452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T20:20:32.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  死臭雞"}]}